ret_cn": "ClinVar数据库无记录，其与肿瘤发生发展的相关性暂不明确。", "variant_interpret_en": "", "variant_desc_cn": "该变异为同义突变。", "variant_desc_en": "", "evidence_categorys": "", "evi_sum": [], "drug_var": {"drug_names": [], "var": {"gene_symbol": "PDCD1", "gene_region": "exon5", "hgvs_p_abbr": "p.(Pro262=)", "hgvs_c": "c.786C>T", "hgvs_p": "p.(P262=)"}}, "gene_function": "PDCD1为程序性细胞死亡1，编码受体PD-1，在免疫细胞上表达，并与配体PD-L1和PD-L2相互作用后对免疫反应产生抑制作用（PMID: 26681673， PMID: 24403232）。肿瘤治疗中抑制PDCD1 （PD-1）可减轻抗肿瘤免疫应答的抑制（PMID: 26325035、PMID: 26681673、PMID: 26320063、PMID: 24403232）。"}, {"sample_id": "S22110442FD01", "order_code": "df2775ee670711ed8a400242ac180006", "bio_category": "Snvindel", "gene_symbol": "CDK4", "transcript_primary": "NM_000075.4", "var_id": "78cee2df68f8dea058dc71299664f1f4", "hgvs_c": "c.763C>T", "hgvs_p": "p.R255C", "hgvs_p_abbr": "p.Arg255Cys", "chr": "chr12", "start": "58143021", "end": "58143021", "ref": "G", "alt": "A", "gene_region": "exon7", "freq": 0.4737, "freq_case": null, "freq_ctrl": null, "freq_ss": 0.5004, "freq_sc": null, "type": "nonSynonymous_Substitution", "tag": "PASS;PW;WBC", "igvplot": "/var/www/html/report_backend/system_files/json_file/20221126_SHXW_A000880_ADXPAN116_v0.3.0.export20221126181911/S22110442FD01_S22110442FD01L01_BH7KG7DRX2_1/IGV/chr12_58143021_58143021.svg", "depth": 2985.0, "json_batch_name": "20221126_SHXW_A000880_ADXPAN116_v0.3.0.export20221126181911", "var_origin": "", "clinical_significance": "Uncertain", "function_classification": "Uncertain", "clinical_category": "Tier III", "literature": "31159747", "polymorphism": "Non-Polymorphism", "variant_interpret_cn": "该变异在ExAC、gnomADe、gnomADg数据库EAS人群频率分别为0.0006933（6/8654）、0.0006525（12/18392）、0.001282（2/1560），1000G数据库无记录；在有乳腺癌和/或卵巢癌家族史的个人（PMID: 31159747）中曾有报道。该变异在ClinVar数据库报道为Conflicting_interpretations_of_pathogenicity（Uncertain_significance,Benign,Likely_benign）（ID=133877，可靠度为一颗星）。基于整合预测工具REVEL认为该变异为neutral。", "variant_interpret_en": "", "variant_desc_cn": "该变异为错义突变，导致基因编码蛋白第255位氨基酸由精氨酸突变为半胱氨酸。", "variant_desc_en": "", "evidence_categorys": "BP4", "evi_sum": [], "drug_var": {"drug_names": [], "var": {"gene_symbol": "CDK4", "gene_region": "exon7", "hgvs_p_abbr": "p.Arg255Cys", "hgvs_c": "c.763C>T", "hgvs_p": "p.R255C"}}, "gene_function": "CDK4（细胞周期蛋白依赖性激酶4），是细胞周期G1-S期转变的关键调控因子，可抑制细胞衰老和凋亡（PMID: 24089445），也是黑色素瘤中T细胞识别的肿瘤抗原（PMID: 29403496）。 CDK4失调可促进多种肿瘤发生（PMID: 24795392），在脂肪肉瘤(PMID: 23569312)和子宫肉瘤(PMID: 32156473)中常见CDK4扩增。 "}, {"sample_id": "S22110442FD01", "order_code": "df2775ee670711ed8a400242ac180006", "bio_category": "Snvindel", "gene_symbol": "BCL2L11", "transcript_primary": "NM_138621.5", "var_id": "50f50cee7d3efa02be647441960c576d", "hgvs_c": "c.394+1479_394+4381del", "hgvs_p": "p.?", "hgvs_p_abbr": "p.?", "chr": "chr2", "start": "111883195", "end": "111886097", "ref": "2903", "alt": "-", "gene_region": "intron2", "freq": 0.1886, "freq_case": null, "freq_ctrl": null, "freq_ss": 0.1299, "freq_sc": null, "type": "Intronic", "tag": "PASS;HotSpot", "igvplot": "/var/www/html/report_backend/system_files/json_file/20221126_SHXW_A000880_ADXPAN116_v0.3.0.export20221126181911/S22110442FD01_S22110442FD01L01_BH7KG7DRX2_1/IGV/chr2_111883195_111886097.svg", "depth": 2301.0, "json_batch_name": "20221126_SHXW_A000880_ADXPAN116_v0.3.0.export20221126181911", "var_origin": "", "clinical_significance": "Uncertain", "function_classification": "Uncertain", "clinical_category": "Tier III", "literature": "28717678,26767045,26271547,27926478,32508032,22426421", "polymorphism": "Non-Polymorphism", "variant_interpret_cn": "目前该变异的临床意义仍存在较大争议，有研究认为该变异与EGFR-TKI的耐药有关（PMID: 22426421, PMID: 27926478, PMID: 26767045），但也有一些与其矛盾的研究（PMID: 26271547, PMID: 28717678, PMID: 32508032），其中吴一龙团队2020年发表的文章表明该变异与一代、二代、三代EGFR TKIs治疗疗效受损没有关系（PMID: 32508032）。", "variant_interpret_en": "", "variant_desc_cn": "该变异为内含子区突变。", "variant_desc_en": "", "evidence_categorys": "", "evi_sum": [], "drug_var": {"drug_names": [], "var": {"gene_symbol": "BCL2L11", "gene_region": "intron2", "hgvs_p_abbr": "p.?", "hgvs_c": "c.394+1479_394+4381del", "hgvs_p": "p.?"}}, "gene_function": "BCL2L11，BCL2样11，是BCL2家族中激活细胞凋亡的程序化细胞死亡调节因子的一员（PMID:26405162）。BCL2L11的下调在包括淋巴瘤和结直肠癌在内的各种癌症中被发现（PMID:26405162），并且与非小细胞肺癌对酪氨酸激酶抑制剂治疗的耐药性有关（PMID:26325082）。"}], "sv": [], "cnv": [], "cnv_file_path": {"sample_id": "S22110442FD01", "abs_path": "/var/www/html/report_backend/system_files/json_file/20221126_SHXW_A000880_ADXPAN116_v0.3.0.export20221126181911/S22110442FD01_S22110442FD01L01_BH7KG7DRX2_1/S22110442FD01_S22110442FD01L01_BH7KG7DRX2_1_LC76.cnv.png"}, "rna_sv": [], "mlpa": [], "hrd": [], "msi": [{"sample_id": "", "order_code": "df2775ee670711ed8a400242ac180006", "var_id": "MSS", "msi_score": 0.0577, "img_path": "/var/www/html/report_backend/system_files/json_file/20221126_SHXW_A000880_ADXPAN116_v0.3.0.export20221126181911/S22110442FD01_S22110442FD01L01_BH7KG7DRX2_1/S22110442FD01_S22110442FD01L01_BH7KG7DRX2_1.msi.png", "variant_interpret_cn": "", "variant_interpret_en": "", "variant_desc_cn": "微卫星（Microsatellite）又称简单重复序列（SSR），是指遍布于人类基因组中的短串联重复序列，一般由1-6个核苷酸组成。DNA复制时，肿瘤细胞内的微卫星由于重复单位的插入或缺失而造成的微卫星长度的变化，称为微卫星不稳定性（Microsatellite Instability, MSI）。大量研究表明，MSI是由错配修复（mismatch repair，MMR）基因突变或功能缺陷引起的（PMID: 25701956）。MSI在多种癌种中被发现，包括子宫内膜癌、结直肠癌和胃腺癌等。据报道，10%-15%的散发性结直肠癌患者存在MSI（PMID: 15528785），NCCN指南明确推荐所有结直肠癌患者均需考虑做MSI或MMR检测。临床上也已将MSI作为结直肠癌及其他实体瘤预后和制定辅助治疗方案的重要分子标志物。", "variant_desc_en": "", "evi_sum": [], "drug_var": {"drug_names": [], "var": {"biomarker_type": "MSS"}}}], "tmb": [], "pdl1": [], "knb": [], "ec_type": [], "cdx": [{"gene_symbol": "ALK", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "BRAF", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "EGFR", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "ERBB2", "tumor_group_id": "1", "tumor_name_cn": "非小细胞肺癌", "tumor_name_en": "Non-Small Cell Lung Cancer"}, {"gene_symbol": "KRA